{"tid":1606001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日印尼 we connect","createTime":"2019-09-30T12:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T13:36:40.000Z","uid":173627,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45c004160872ee12d0acb54de27b86831c758b94","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"近排印尼反禁同性戀法遊行俾當地警方濫暴鎮壓，有兩名學生犧牲咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日又有黑警射印尼記者，心痛之餘，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地同印尼依家有共同敵人</span>，呢個係我地吸納印傭做新戰友嘅好機會！係本身星期日已經會係中環聚集嘅印傭呀！ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我建議聽日遊行要做呢啲嘢：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 聲援印尼示威<br />\n基本嘢要做，舉牌嗌口號，唔知嗰邊發生緊咩事嘅請睇立場： <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/印尼抗爭兩學生死亡-總統籲警方克制-示威者向港人學習應對催淚彈/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%B1%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%85%8B%E5%88%B6-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6q3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=77a5add4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%B1%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%85%8B%E5%88%B6-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%2F&h=2b074709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/印尼抗爭兩學生死亡-總統籲警方克制-示威者向港人學習應對催淚彈/</a> <br />\n<br />\n2. 支持受傷印尼記者<br />\n收到風尋日印尼記者俾黑警射眼之後全港印傭震怒，黑警嘗試淡化件事，即係佢地驚我地發大件事，咁我地一定要狙擊！大大力打落去！<br />\n<br />\n3. 追悼印尼學生<br />\n冇乜好講，諗起都嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日同你個印傭姐姐一齊行！一齊招募新戰友！<br />\n長遠向印尼輸出社運經驗！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"46a59e82cc1cb9fdb44b850b816cb7f3b503d23c","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"621bce6def0ce792060be91ba23769de70eab015","tid":1606001,"uid":164585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1日所有偽勇武既唔該企番後面 同散開小小</span></span>"},{"pid":"219685730c068e0fcd69660d1a72639925367f55","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"印傭 we connect!"},{"pid":"1a9555254620a15440f23b963bfb06b4c98a01df","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"印傭 we connect!"},{"pid":"fbf4ee1548ec701ed080cd13abd806a48618ae63","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:35:07.000Z","msg":"印傭 we connect!"},{"pid":"fe5254a97e48061bf3246ba1458f1d3277c9d018","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"印傭 we connect!"},{"pid":"b48856215ad5b5de200f839df50dd1e40760c575","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"印傭 we connect!"},{"pid":"6b6f1c756deddfc7bf46b62fc09a5a2439ccd903","tid":1606001,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"排華3.0"},{"pid":"a11384ec78f827861dca7f209fa6d9baad1e6758","tid":1606001,"uid":61161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"掘磚嘅你哋...點解唔一人一罐可樂？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db04188d7e6d6334173dbf453d071b74627a6835","tid":1606001,"uid":173627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"